  ('dietitian-moex-01725', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-108-cd594556', 'sub-dietitian-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列有關單醣在小腸吸收的敘述何者正確？', '["葡萄糖經小腸絨毛上的GLUT2轉運載體吸收進入小腸細胞，不消耗能量", "小腸細胞內大部分的葡萄糖經由Na+/K+ATPase提供能量，由SGLT1轉運載體送入血液", "果糖由GLUT5轉運載體送進小腸，再經GLUT2轉運進入血液，不消耗能量", "胰島素會活化葡萄糖的轉運載體GLUT2，促進小腸快速的吸收葡萄糖"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:57+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "35bf5c93d082", "answer_pdf_sha1": "ac94409250aa", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "108020", "c": "103", "s": "0202", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "營養學", "year": "108", "exam_name": "108年第一次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 2, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-01726', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-108-cd594556', 'sub-dietitian-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列敘述何者不是纖維的特性？', '["水溶性纖維可被大腸內的細菌消化", "果膠是一種非澱粉的多醣類", "半纖維素不屬於多醣類", "多數的纖維是由單醣聚合而成的"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:57+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "35bf5c93d082", "answer_pdf_sha1": "ac94409250aa", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "108020", "c": "103", "s": "0202", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "營養學", "year": "108", "exam_name": "108年第一次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 3, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-01727', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-108-cd594556', 'sub-dietitian-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列何種食物含有最多天然果糖？', '["番茄", "蜂蜜", "奇異果", "牛奶"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:57+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "35bf5c93d082", "answer_pdf_sha1": "ac94409250aa", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "108020", "c": "103", "s": "0202", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "營養學", "year": "108", "exam_name": "108年第一次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 4, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-01728', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-108-cd594556', 'sub-dietitian-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '人體在下列那一種情況最有可能處於正氮平衡（positive nitrogen balance）？', '["敗血症", "長期節食", "懷孕後期", "高燒不退"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:57+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "35bf5c93d082", "answer_pdf_sha1": "ac94409250aa", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "108020", "c": "103", "s": "0202", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "營養學", "year": "108", "exam_name": "108年第一次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 5, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
